{"tid":1489162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙利肺出事 即時入院接受特別治療","createTime":"2019-08-19T21:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:21:18.000Z","uid":165817,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96f1a40c579821a957fbccc37af2fccdcceec5f0","tid":1489162,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T21:29:25.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯證實，此前遭受流感侵襲的領隊沙利患上肺炎，需要接受「特別的治療」。<br />\n<br />\n沙利此前由於流感，沒有隨隊前往泰利斯天拿參加友誼賽。今天沙利雖然回到訓練基地，但仍然無法指揮祖雲達斯球員訓練。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯其後證實，沙利在下午接受了進一步檢查後，確認患上了肺炎，需接受特別治療。<br />\n<br />\n他已經授權球會通報其健康狀況，至於否現場指揮本週末對陣帕爾馬的首週意甲比賽，目前仍然有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，沙利有非常嚴重的煙癮，這可能會進一步影響到其身體狀況。"},{"pid":"592e973eb894da49ff6b037124bfcc16dd9b28b8","tid":1489162,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T21:51:29.000Z","msg":"珍重"},{"pid":"b292b60366712226115095e846fe8422f7aa0e6f","tid":1489162,"uid":19638,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:39:38.000Z","msg":"一日食百幾二百包煙"},{"pid":"1af30f30865bf88110bf4522bf6605cb3c9392d8","tid":1489162,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b292b60366712226115095e846fe8422f7aa0e6f","tid":1489162,"uid":19638,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:39:38.000Z","msg":"一日食百幾二百包煙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:43:07.000Z","msg":"又唔見我同牙路 有事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b021a2e0df3fd74a1a23cb12cc6a20e2a2681a","tid":1489162,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"唔係話戒左咩呢排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e04ce8a1a9fda405203cd532e7610abb9557691","tid":1489162,"uid":37948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"weak...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禾地d ching個個weekend食催淚彈都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi